{"tid":2087775,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【維修費逾12萬】東莞4名頑童手多多劃花45架車　家長：他們不懂事","createTime":"2020-06-30T21:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T04:22:53.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"acca7e4818607eb42fc6e6af02683fc03105bd81","tid":2087775,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T21:23:57.000Z","msg":"近日在廣東東莞，有關「4名孩子劃花數十架車被索賠150萬」的消息引起網民熱議，報道指被劃花的私家車中不乏寶馬、Lincoln、平治等豪車。<br />\n<br />\n針對此事，東莞市公安局樟木頭分局周一（6月29日）發布情況通報稱，經調查發現，4名兒童撿起路邊石塊將45架私家車劃花，其中37架車維修價格約12萬元（人民幣．下同），尚有8輛未提供報價。涉事孩童的家長其後現身公開道歉，並表示願意積極承擔相應責任。<br />\n<br />\n綜合內媒報道，事發在6月21日，東莞某屋苑路旁兩側有多架私家車車被劃損。有屋苑居民透露，此處停車位一直非常緊拙，很多次車都停在屋苑內道路的一側。「這些車是被鋒利的東西畫出了花，已經不是簡單的劃車了。涉事的小孩有4個，十多歲的樣子。」另一名居民回憶，部分私家車的車身大範圍都被孩子畫上了圖案，有的還在車頭上直接「塗鴉」污言穢語。<br />\n<br />\n其中一名私家車被劃花的車主表示，屋苑並沒有收取任何停車費，所以車主們普遍認為和物業管理沒有太大關係，「當天跟著幾位車主去派出所的時候，4個小孩看起來挺淡定的，並沒有受到甚麼教訓。家長們仍不聞不問，沒打過一個道歉的電話。」還有一名車主說，目前車主和物業報警並聘請了律師，準備通過司法途徑解決問題。<br />\n<br />\n根據警方最新的通報，目前四名兒童的監護人對兒童的行為進行了批評教育，公開向遭受損失的車主道歉，並表示願意積極承擔相應責任。涉事孩童的家長現身公開道歉時，其中一位家長表示，「對不起每一位車主，孩子不懂事 導致造成傷害，希望能夠共同和平解決事件。」<br />\n<br />\n網民熱議：<br />\n「孩子不懂事，家長懂事就行。」<br />\n「賠錢了大人才會心痛，才能好好教育」<br />\n「家長沒有反思自己的教育問題。」<br />\n「不在乎你孩子懂不懂事，照價賠錢就行了。」<br />\n「家長的道歉是一個積極的態度，監護人承擔一切責任就好。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200630/354727314149478401.png/vCngzGM51XUHDw80uNuU-_K_A86BplKirpLN_a6Szf0?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200630%2F354727314149478401.png%2FvCngzGM51XUHDw80uNuU-_K_A86BplKirpLN_a6Szf0%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=f3e9b092&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200630/354725882889375744.png/SJSD5LCIOOwBhrn3546tJIGdZ33Hzo0lEFewZhBXsGY?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200630%2F354725882889375744.png%2FSJSD5LCIOOwBhrn3546tJIGdZ33Hzo0lEFewZhBXsGY%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=aa8205a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200630/354725959347343360.jpeg/1UKwCwDIde427n7KL0gQ12ppTXc2-zoyh-mcXYfpnF0?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200630%2F354725959347343360.jpeg%2F1UKwCwDIde427n7KL0gQ12ppTXc2-zoyh-mcXYfpnF0%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=16113bbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200630/354726483052335104.jpeg/3LfYGZ4sOqKdnkvcU3g2ISixLFNvu6_9PaMlDz2jJQ8?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200630%2F354726483052335104.jpeg%2F3LfYGZ4sOqKdnkvcU3g2ISixLFNvu6_9PaMlDz2jJQ8%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=b960b38c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200630/354726485208207360.jpeg/N_-hyq5fLFKHRwe3AYILXOoyaG1lASdRyjIwCMoyMAg?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200630%2F354726485208207360.jpeg%2FN_-hyq5fLFKHRwe3AYILXOoyaG1lASdRyjIwCMoyMAg%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=c0e26a51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200630/354725961557741568.png/vXlyV67L6rMGZvicrh4GPxXozFFxFe4ondjZIZ3Y2SE?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200630%2F354725961557741568.png%2FvXlyV67L6rMGZvicrh4GPxXozFFxFe4ondjZIZ3Y2SE%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=3f44c082&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01c402fb64f55c240161944d832186f1e60fbadc","tid":2087775,"uid":2545,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T21:26:33.000Z","msg":"他們只是個孩子呀.jpg"},{"pid":"5b128d60689d4ecc037b2f04f73e134de6bb7696","tid":2087775,"uid":1348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T21:29:55.000Z","msg":"你係唔係中国人！？"},{"pid":"ae996d854b9ae8208a8a1a3ae03cdb82d313a568","tid":2087775,"uid":200083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T21:31:13.000Z","msg":"幼蝗拎去生滾就差唔多"},{"pid":"6630de7c7d4