/>\n「賠錢了大人才會心痛，才能好好教育」<br />\n「家長沒有反思自己的教育問題。」<br />\n「不在乎你孩子懂不懂事，照價賠錢就行了。」<br />\n「家長的道歉是一個積極的態度，監護人承擔一切責任就好。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200630/354727314149478401.png/vCngzGM51XUHDw80uNuU-_K_A86BplKirpLN_a6Szf0?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200630%2F354727314149478401.png%2FvCngzGM51XUHDw80uNuU-_K_A86BplKirpLN_a6Szf0%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=f3e9b092&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200630/354725882889375744.png/SJSD5LCIOOwBhrn3546tJIGdZ33Hzo0lEFewZhBXsGY?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200630%2F354725882889375744.png%2FSJSD5LCIOOwBhrn3546tJIGdZ33Hzo0lEFewZhBXsGY%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=aa8205a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200630/354725959347343360.jpeg/1UKwCwDIde427n7KL0gQ12ppTXc2-zoyh-mcXYfpnF0?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200630%2F354725959347343360.jpeg%2F1UKwCwDIde427n7KL0gQ12ppTXc2-zoyh-mcXYfpnF0%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=16113bbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200630/354726483052335104.jpeg/3LfYGZ4sOqKdnkvcU3g2ISixLFNvu6_9PaMlDz2jJQ8?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200630%2F354726483052335104.jpeg%2F3LfYGZ4sOqKdnkvcU3g2ISixLFNvu6_9PaMlDz2jJQ8%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=b960b38c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200630/354726485208207360.jpeg/N_-hyq5fLFKHRwe3AYILXOoyaG1lASdRyjIwCMoyMAg?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200630%2F354726485208207360.jpeg%2FN_-hyq5fLFKHRwe3AYILXOoyaG1lASdRyjIwCMoyMAg%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=c0e26a51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media